mortal kombat : rebirth is a 2010 detailed short film directed by kevin tancharoen , with fight choreography by larnell stovall , who also choreographed undisputed iii : redemption . based on the mortal kombat series of fighting games , the short-film " actually was made by the director to sell warner bros. on his vision for a reimagined mortal kombat film . " the pitch eventually evolved into the web series mortal kombat : legacy and solidified tancharoen 's directing duties on warner bros . mortal kombat feature film . the short-film features an alternative version of the mortal kombat universe . the characters of the game are portrayed with vastly different origins , based on realism . there is no mention of outworld or any other supernatural elements , although the tournament itself is a main part of the storyline in this short . tancharoen himself has noted that he would n't shy away from supernatural elements entirely , but they have to be " done in a very tasteful way " .